      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The John Carter Glenn Collection consists primarily of cards autographed by composers, musical performers, and instrument makers. The Collection also holds 4 autograph letters: 1 letter from Georg Gemünder to Jesse Weissman, and 1 letter each from Victor Herbert, Moritz Moszkowski, and Anton Seidl, all to Albert Weissman.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
